prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card design, flat 2D vector art, clean illustration style. A charming and humorous cartoon scene featuring a couple. The man is playfully presenting a ridiculously oversized, beautifully wrapped birthday gift box to the woman, who looks on with a delighted and comically surprised expression, hands clasped to her cheeks. The gift box is wrapped in simple pastel paper with an elegant ribbon. The figures are drawn with simple lines and elegant shapes, wearing casual, solid-colored clothing. The entire scene is set against a clean, solid cream-colored background, emphasizing the characters and the humorous interaction. In the center, in a beautiful, readable, dark gray handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Hope it's as amazing as you are."
